    "Publication bias was evaluated using a funnel plot and Egger's test.",
    "The statistical heterogeneity was estimated through the use of the Q test and incoherence index (I2).",
    "Moreover, Meta-regression was employed to assess the source of the heterogeneity among included the studies.",
    "The effect size calculation involved the utilization of a random effects model for 95% CI.",
    "The statistical analysis was performed using Stata version 17.0 software."
